==製作==
2015年2月5日，[[蓋·皮爾斯|蓋·皮爾斯]]和[[蜜雅·娃絲柯思卡|蜜雅·娃絲柯思卡]]被宣布加入電影的演出<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=43370|title=Guy Pearce Heads For Brimstone|accessdate=May 25, 2015|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924130611/http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=43370|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後來，[[羅伯·派汀森|羅伯·派汀森]]和[[卡莉絲·范·荷登|卡莉絲·范·荷登]]加入詮釋罪犯的角色<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=43396|title=Robert Pattinson Fired Up For Brimstone|accessdate=May 25, 2015|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924130616/http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=43396|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/casting-robert-pattinson-ready-for-brimstone-nicolas-cage-boards-uss-indianapolis-more-20150209|title=Casting: Robert Pattinson Ready For 'Brimstone,' Nicolas Cage Boards ‘USS Indianapolis’ & More|accessdate=May 25, 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150525163455/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/casting-robert-pattinson-ready-for-brimstone-nicolas-cage-boards-uss-indianapolis-more-20150209|archive-date=2015-05-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2015年5月，導演{{link-en|馬丁·寇霍文|Martin Koolhoven}}確認傑克·羅斯的參演<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.brimstonethemovie.com/media?mediaId=19633746|title=BrimstoneMovie|accessdate=May 25, 2015|archive-date=2018-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180814232850/http://www.brimstonethemovie.com/media?mediaId=19633746|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年6月，《[[好萊塢報導|好萊塢報導]]》證實，[[達科塔·芬妮|達科塔·芬妮]]與[[基特·哈靈頓|基特·哈靈頓]]加入並取代娃絲柯思卡和派汀森的角色<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/kit-harington-joins-thriller-brimstone-804716?utm_source=twitter|title=BrimstoneMovie|accessdate=June 23, 2015|archive-date=2015-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150915125533/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/kit-harington-joins-thriller-brimstone-804716?utm_source=twitter|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

